caption.text: When I posted this in stories a team member said, “you’re making it look like it’s easy, but you’re the hardest working person I think I’ve ever met”. So please don’t think that I’m saying it’s easy. BUT, I am saying that you might be closer than you think. I am saying that small changes can lead to radically different outcomes. I am saying, I can help you win on social much, much faster than you would alone. If that sounds like something you want and if you’re all in, comment BOOTCAMP and I’ll send you some info about Viral Video Bootcamp

clips_metadata.reusable_text_attribute_string: 3 tips that’ll make you more confident on camera

reusable_text_info.text: 3 tips that’ll make you more confident on camera

caption.text:
Trust me, I’ve been to the edge. I’ve lived through my version of hell. But I managed to turn my life around. Because one person had belief in me through even when all the evidence pointed to me being a ‘failure’. That one person spurred me on through the dark moments. And allowed me to try enough things for long enough to finally win. I hope this message can be that glimmer of hope for you. That thing that gets you to just keep going. Even when the going gets tough. The past does not decide your future. 

#failure #motivation #mindset
